title: Single-Cell RNAseq analysis of diffuse neoplastic infiltrating cells at the migrating front of human glioblastoma
abstract: We used single-cell RNAseq to investigate the heterogeneity of glioblastoma tumors and assess differential expression between cells within and in proximity of the tumor.
overall_design: Examination of cell types in human primary glioblastoma samples.
summary: We used single-cell RNAseq to investigate the heterogeneity of glioblastoma tumors and assess differential expression between cells within and in proximity of the tumor.
